---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Men haqimda - Shavkatov"
  description="Shavkatov haqida - dasturchi va texnologiya ishqibozi"
>
  <article class="about">
    <h1>Men haqimda</h1>

    <p>
      Salom! Men Shavkatov. Bu blogda men texnologiya, dasturlash va shaxsiy
      tajribalarim haqida yozaman.
    </p>

    <p>
      Bu yerni o'zingiz haqingizda ma'lumot bilan to'ldiring. Quyidagi
      bo'limlarni qo'shishingiz mumkin:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Qiziqishlaringiz</li>
      <li>Tajribangiz</li>
      <li>Maqsadlaringiz</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Aloqa</h2>
    <p>
      Men bilan bog'lanish uchun quyidagi platformalardan foydalanishingiz mumkin:
    </p>

    <ul class="social-links">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/shavkatov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/shavkatov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:hello@shavkatov.io">Email</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .social-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .social-links a {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
